title: Grateful Dead Live at Autzen Stadium - University of Oregon on 1990-06-23
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6 MHz) >KORG AudioGate 4 > Samplitude Pro X3 Suite > FLAC/24
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger-> West L.A. Fadeaway, Me & My Uncle, Cumberland Blues, Far From Me, They Love Each Other, Cassidy, Tennessee Jed, Promised Land

Set 2

Eyes Of The World, Looks Like Rain-> Crazy Fingers-> Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Jam-> The Wheel-> I Need A Miracle-> Morning Dew, E: One More Saturday Night

reviews.review_text:
Must play the Eyes This whole show kicks ass, but you must check out the Eyes. Absolute perfection. 

Excellent sound quality. I love the punchy Phil bass front and center.
